{"tid":1883534,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[代post] 跪求讀緊中六既同學入黎幫手填份問卷","createTime":"2020-02-17T04:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T07:26:26.000Z","uid":49042,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"afbc935df6edc3d3c15724aa73615b76f6f92382","tid":1883534,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T04:28:42.000Z","msg":"代Post, 有咩聯絡番佢tg: <a href=\"https://t.me/cuhk2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcuhk2020&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ6joMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=f79d3bd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/cuhk2020</a><br />\n<br />\n是咁的 我喺中大做緊個project 想邀請中六同學幫手填份問卷<br />\n因為外國D研究好多都集中睇academic performance<br />\n所以我地個project主要係想研究番香港本地中六同學既社交生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家我地已經有超過700人填左 但係仲差50個人<br />\n求連登仔幫下手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n詳情同條link係呢度：<a href=\"http://cuhk.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_dn9B33tqUDw9lQh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcuhk.au1.qualtrics.com%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_dn9B33tqUDw9lQh&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ6joMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=f7fd5cb2\" target=\"_blank\">http://cuhk.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_dn9B33tqUDw9lQh</a><br />\n想知多D就TG我：<a href=\"https://t.me/cuhk2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcuhk2020&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ6joMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=f79d3bd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/cuhk2020</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WBf4Aii.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWBf4Aii.jpg&h=db69e0e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86c912ef2d15c19b53d463b108f9e963a4e92eda","tid":1883534,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:44:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"057413b5